  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育LMS系统绘制一个连接流程图，核心是课堂服务与门户之间的数据包交互。我想从客户端门户开始，包含GradeSync、ContentCDN和学生数据库这几个模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，客户端侧我标记为Education_LMS_Portal，内部包含C1到C5五个节点。C1和C5都用GradeSync，C2是ContentCDN，C3是学生数据库，C4是门户本身。这样安排可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "C4",
        "C5",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，C1和C5都用GradeSync是因为GradeSync在流程中会出现两次——一次在连接建立阶段，一次在确认阶段。服务器侧需要ClassroomService，里面要有ContentCDN的判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C5",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，服务器侧我设置为Education_ClassroomService，内部S1是ContentCDN，S2我做成菱形判断节点也是ContentCDN，S3和S5、S6都是LMS门户，S4是ClassroomService本身。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5",
        "S6",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连接流程这样设计：C1到C2到C3，然后连到S1，这是初始请求链。S1收到后要判断有效性，无效的话直接丢弃到Drop节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "S1",
        "Drop",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，C1→C2→C3→S1是一条链，然后S1分出一条标记为invalid的分支到Drop节点，Drop也是ClassroomService对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "S1",
        "Drop",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Drop就是ClassroomService的丢弃处理。有效的话S1连到S2判断节点，S2根据条件分支：yes走S3→S4→C5，no走S5。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5",
        "C5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已画好：S1→S2，S2标注yes→S3→S4→C5，S2标注no→S5。这里C5是客户端的GradeSync，用于回传确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5",
        "C5",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
