      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "ExplicitACK也是ContentCDN对吧？所以C5→piggyback→S1，以及C5→no_outgoing→ExplicitACK→S1。这样双路径确认机制就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C5",
